  <brief_title>Reduction of Corneal Astigmatism With Toric Intraocular Lens Implantation in Congenital Cataract</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reduction of Corneal Astigmatism With Toric Intraocular Lens Implantation : Early Results in Patients With Congenital Cataract</official_title>
